description: Collects Hawkeye (2016) #13-16, Generations: Hawkeye & Hawkeye #1, West Coast Avengers (2018) #1-4.  The adventures of Hawkeye and Hawkeye! Kate Bishop embarks on an intergenerational adventure through time with a young Clint Barton — in the middle of a battle royale of Marvel’s greatest sharpshooters! Back in the present, Kate reaches out to her old pal Clint for assistance with a problem — but, typically, he needs her help more! Clint’s gotten himself into some big trouble, and that means both Hawkeyes must run a wild race across Los Angeles, trying to stay one step ahead of deadly foes! And the fun has just begun when Kate recruits an all-new team of West Coast Avengers! Say hello to America Chavez! Kid Omega! Gwenpool! And some guy named Fuse! Can this wild new team survive the attack of…the 50-foot Tigra?!
